        </span>
        <span class="cream-release-notes__count">13件</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="cream-release-notes__body">
        <p class="cream-release-notes__intro body-medium">モバイル carousel、画像品質、alt fallback、LCP、不要 asset 削減を改善。</p>
        <ul class="cream-release-notes__list body-medium">
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Collection list、Tab collection、Featured blog posts などの mobile horizontal carousel を native scrolling に寄せて滑らかにしました。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Tab collection 切り替え時に page-wide resize を避け、必要な navigation / overflow のみ更新。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Hero video の uploaded video preview image を初期 poster として表示し、最初の section では優先読み込み。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">YouTube player code と Google Maps を必要になるまで遅延読み込み。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Wishlist page 専用 CSS と shared wishlist UI CSS を分離。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">global jQuery と Remixicon stylesheet を layout から削除。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">shared image helper に responsive sizes、loading、fetchpriority を追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Collection list / Tab collection / Resource images の desktop image quality と lazy-loaded sizes を改善。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Hero、Hero video poster、Shop the look、collection cards、featured blog images に alt fallback を追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Before/After と Map の fallback images を optimized JPG に変更し async decoding を追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Quick add script と page transition hint を設定有効時のみ出力。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Hero schema translation key を追加し Theme Check を通過。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">不要な .DS_Store、backup script、Remixicon assets、PNG fallback assets を削除。</li>
        </ul>
