      <div class="cream-release-notes__body">
        <p class="cream-release-notes__intro body-medium">Slideshow の media、height、transition、navigation を強化。</p>
        <ul class="cream-release-notes__list body-medium">
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">各 slide に desktop / mobile image/video setting を追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">section-level desktop / mobile height controls を Hero video と揃えて追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">slide、fade、zoom-out、wipe の transition style options を追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">non-scroll transition style でも drag で切り替えられる swipe support を追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Button block に left / center / right alignment controls を追加。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">Show navigation arrows on hover の位置と表示条件を整理。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">不要な None navigation option と Full width padded size option を削除。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">previous-slide navigation の wipe direction を修正。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">block-level media height settings を削除し section-level height に統一。</li>
          <li class="cream-release-notes__item">duplicate Theme Editor block attributes を整理し、mobile height label を translation key 化。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
